          <h2>We need your help</h2>
          <p>
            Processing Community Day will be a new way for us work on our goals, and we need your help to make it happen. If you would like to donate or become a Processing Foundation member, <a href="https://processingfoundation.org/support" target="_blank">please do so here</a>.
          </p>
          <p>
            If you or your organization is interested in becoming a sponsor of Processing Community Day and would like to learn more, contact us at <a href="mailto:day@processing.org" target="_blank">day@processing.org</a>.
